\[\beta(\sigma)=P_{\sigma}\left\{\frac{\sum(X_{i}-\bar{X})^{2}}{\sigma^{2}}\leq \frac{C_{0}\sigma_{0}^{2}}{\sigma^{2}}\right\}=\int_{0}^{C_{0}\sigma_{0}^{2}/ \sigma^{2}}\chi_{n-1}^{2}(y)\,dy.\]

