\[n\sum_{j=1}^{k}\frac{1}{\pi_{j}}\left(\frac{Y_{j}}{n}-\pi_{j}\right)^{2}+\frac {n}{\pi_{k+1}}\sum_{i=1}^{k}\sum_{j=1}^{k}\left(\frac{Y_{i}}{n}-\pi_{i}\right) \left(\frac{Y_{j}}{n}-\pi_{j}\right)\.\]

