\[\limsup_{n\to\infty}\inf\left\{E_{\pi+hn^{-1/2}}(\phi_{n}):\ \sum_{i=1}^{k+1} \frac{h_{i}^{2}}{\pi_{i}}\geq b^{2},\ \pi+hn^{-1/2}\in\Omega\right\}\]

\[\leq P\{\chi_{k}^{2}(b^{2})>c_{k,1-\alpha}\}. \tag{16.23}\]

